{"tid":2490590,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ViuTV] Chill Club年度推介20/21 星期日 20:00 (1) 人人樂壇 音樂第一","createTime":"2021-04-15T16:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T05:11:30.000Z","uid":30294,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b55ff0e577af3182c6e9e2cab303b2410d8b64e5","tid":2490590,"uid":30294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://chillclub.viu.tv/og-image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchillclub.viu.tv%2Fog-image.jpg&h=86326301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nChill Club 推介榜年度推介20/21<br />\n香港ViuTV主辦的首屆本地流行音樂頒獎典禮，於2021年4月18日晚上8時假九龍灣國際展貿中心E-Max匯星舉行，由趙學而、駱振偉擔任司儀，主題爲「人人樂壇，音樂第一」，評選範圍爲2020年5月31日（2020年第22週）至2021年2月28日（2021年第9週）「Chill Club 推介榜」的上榜歌曲及歌手。除幕後獎項外，各大獎項均由全港市民一人一票投票產生。<br />\n本次頒獎典禮由「FWD富衛保險」冠名贊助。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVMhFpKTs16dTZe968LMFuXqjW5UScAfArp5FpbhocRYH?filename=uMXCbwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuMXCbwz.jpg&h=c84e3c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZXxE5w186mc3ZKXmbYSMMEv9ePxgCKVmd6yv4sNggDFU?filename=s9k8ibz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs9k8ibz.jpg&h=eac2ac1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fcadadf63538a440ad8199013055e63bbd4f9da","tid":2490590,"uid":30294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:48:42.000Z","msg":"入圍名單<br />\n<strong><ins>Chill Club年度男歌手</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ59Lrhte1kFxSiG4CXrYVRXWwend54UwifLhhDfQJ4aF?filename=iJDZzwP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiJDZzwP.png&h=04817a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Chill Club年度女歌手</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXhJvM3hk1mr3meCGMoeA1Gzxu1k6Yg2HasAp1vu84qSz?filename=DkBgBLh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDkBgBLh.png