Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=b16c95b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://viu.tv/chillclub</a><br />\n<br />\n人人樂壇，音樂第一， 星期日晚見！<br />\n<br />\nP.S.如果認證手提電話號碼時，畫面顯示「此電話號碼已被登記」，可以試下搵返過往參與其他ViuTV活動同曾成功驗證嘅會員帳號，以該會員帳號參加活動。如你未曾以其他電郵註冊ViuTV會員並綁定手提電話號碼，請電郵至 help@viu.tv 或致電2239 8899同我哋聯絡啦！<br />\n<br />\n#ChillClub推介榜年度推介<br />\n#人人樂壇音樂第一 #人人樂壇 #音樂第一"},{"pid":"7eb1d3614788a116387e46de6a348f98a5d8da21","tid":2490590,"uid":30294,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.orangenews.hk/common//202103/031114107owg.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.orangenews.hk%2Fcommon%2F%2F202103%2F031114107owg.JPG&h=fbd24a71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b067bea10ef9558b0f9c00f9c0aa57c3c08648e9","tid":2490590,"uid":55390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:57:37.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5c2c70d8d79a58e072b35fa36805be833f3bb8","tid":2490590,"uid":190212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T16:58:21.000Z","msg":"lm支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee595ae419c997aae222c32ec15f88bac4307987","tid":2490590,"uid":175194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:01:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c6c35c53e89b9596b9102358adc617ea5c5b5e31","tid":2490590,"uid":264325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f060e933a635cf0313de5549d1ee4455692bbe